title: THE WALKING DEAD - TYREESE SPECIAL (2013) (Digital) (Zone-Empire
description:
The Walking Dead Tyreese Special

Creators: Robert Kirkman, Charlie Adlard, Cliff Rathburn

Story By: Robert Kirkman
Art By: Charlie Adlard, Cliff Rathburn
Cover By: Charlie Adlard, Dave Stewart

Published: October 9, 2013

Just in time for the premiere of Season Four of the TV show! Tyreese, a character prominently featured in the season, gets a spotlight here. The special issue reprints his first appearance from THE WALKING DEAD #7 as well as his origin story, first printed in THE WALKING DEAD: FREE COMIC BOOK DAY SPECIAL.
